    "dhp62:1": "matthi dhanaṁ matthi → puttā matthi dhanammatthi (bj); puttā matthi dhanamatthi (sya-all); puttamatthi dhanamatthi (mr) | hi → attāpi (?) ",
    "dhp69:1": "Madhuṁvā → madhuvā (bj, sya-all, pts1ed, pts2ed) ",
    "dhp69:4": "atha → atha bālo (bj, sya-all, pts1ed, pts2ed); bālo (mr) ",
    "dhp70:3": "saṅkhātadhammānaṁ → saṅkhatadhammānaṁ (bj, pts1ed, pts2ed, mr) ",
    "dhp71:4": "Bhasmacchannova → bhasmā channova (sya-all, mr); bhasmācchannova (pts1ed, pts2ed) ",
    "dhp72:2": "ñattaṁ → ñāttaṁ (?) ",
    "dhp73:1": "Asantaṁ bhāvanamiccheyya → asantaṁ bhāvamiccheyya (sya-all); asantabhāvanamiccheyya (mr) "
  },
